HEADWORD: Indefinitude
<hw>In`de*fin"i*tude</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>Indefiniteness; vagueness; also, number or quantity not limited by
our understanding, though yet finite.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Sir M. Hale.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Indehiscence</ent>⟦br⟧
